#. Tag: title
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kded6</command> consolidates several small services in one process. "
"These are mostly &DBus; services provided by KDED modules, but it also "
"manages sycoca (a binary cache of servicetypes, &MIME; types and services "
"used by KService) and KConfig update scripts as needed."
msgstr ""
"<command>kded6</command> एकस्मिन् प्रक्रियायां अनेकाः लघुसेवाः एकीकृत्य स्थापयति । एते "
"प्रायः &DBus; KDED मॉड्यूल् द्वारा प्रदत्ताः सेवाः, परन्तु एतत् sycoca (सेवाप्रकारानाम्, "
"&MIME; KService द्वारा प्रयुक्तानां प्रकाराणां सेवानां च द्विचक्रीयसञ्चयम्) अपि च "
"आवश्यकतानुसारं KConfig अपडेट् स्क्रिप्ट् अपि प्रबन्धयति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For sycoca, it monitors the directories containing .desktop files. When a "
"file is added/removed, it waits 5 seconds (in case of a series of updates), "
"and then launches <command>kbuildsycoca6</command> to update the sycoca."
msgstr ""
"sycoca कृते .desktop सञ्चिकाः समाविष्टानि निर्देशिकाः निरीक्षते । यदा सञ्चिका योजिता/"
"निष्कासिता भवति तदा सा ५ सेकेण्ड् प्रतीक्षते (अद्यतनश्रृङ्खलायां), ततः sycoca अद्यतनीकर्तुं "
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> प्रारभते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For KConfig, it checks newly-installed update files, &ie; the *.upd files "
"used to update configuration files of users when the configuration file "
"formats changes, and runs the KConfig update utility to perform the updates."
msgstr ""
"KConfig कृते, एतत् नवस्थापितानि अद्यतनसञ्चिकाः परीक्षते, &ie; *.upd सञ्चिकाः उपयोक्तृणां "
"विन्याससञ्चिकानां अद्यतनीकरणाय प्रयुक्ताः यदा विन्याससञ्चिकास्वरूपाः परिवर्तन्ते, तथा च "
"अद्यतनं कर्तुं KConfig अद्यतन-उपयोगिता चालयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Those tasks are also run when <command>kded6</command> is started to ensure "
"that the user configuration is up to date."
msgstr ""
"तानि कार्याणि तदा अपि चाल्यन्ते यदा <command>kded6</command> आरभ्यते यत् "
"उपयोक्तृविन्यासः अद्यतनः अस्ति इति सुनिश्चितं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You do not normally need to run <command>kded6</command> directly; &plasma; "
"desktop sessions run it automatically, and it is started on demand when an "
"application attempts to use a &DBus; interface provided by it or one of its "
"modules."
msgstr ""
"सामान्यतया भवता <command>kded6</command> प्रत्यक्षतया चालयितुं आवश्यकता नास्ति; "
"&प्लाज्मा; डेस्कटॉप् सत्राणि स्वयमेव चालयन्ति, तथा च यदा अनुप्रयोगः &DBus; तया अथवा तस्य "
"एकेन मॉड्यूलेन प्रदत्तं अन्तरफलकं ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "--check"
msgstr "--अनुशीलय"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the sycoca database, updating it if necessary, and exit."
msgstr "sycoca दत्तांशकोशं पश्यन्तु, आवश्यके सति अद्यतनं कृत्वा, निर्गच्छन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "विन्यासः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<command>kded6</command> can be configured with the <filename>kded6rc</"
#| "filename> ini-style configuration file. On &UNIX; systems, this can be "
#| "found at <filename><varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded6rc</"
#| "filename>; if <varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> is not set, this "
#| "defaults to <filename>~/.config/kded6rc</filename>."
msgid ""
"<command>kded6</command> can be configured with the <filename>kded5rc</"
"filename> ini-style configuration file. On &UNIX; systems, this can be found "
"at <filename><varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded5rc</filename>; if "
"<varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> is not set, this defaults to "
"<filename>~/.config/kded5rc</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<command>kded6</command> इत्येतत् <filename>kded6rc</filename> ini-शैल्याः "
"विन्याससञ्चिकायाः सह विन्यस्तुं शक्यते । &UNIX; प्रणालीषु, एतत् <filename><varname>"
"$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded6rc</filename> इत्यत्र द्रष्टुं शक्यते; यदि <varname>"
"$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> सेट् न भवति तर्हि एतत् <filename>~/.config/kded6rc</"
"filename> इति पूर्वनिर्धारितं भवति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuration file entries are read on-demand, so changes can be made while "
"<command>kded6</command> is running. However, all the current configuration "
"options only really affect the startup behaviour of <command>kded6</command>."
msgstr ""
"विन्याससञ्चिकाप्रविष्टयः आग्रहेण पठ्यन्ते, अतः <command>kded6</command> चालितस्य "
"परिवर्तनं कर्तुं शक्यते । तथापि वर्तमानकाले सर्वे विन्यासविकल्पाः केवलं <command>kded6</"
"command> इत्यस्य आरम्भव्यवहारं वास्तवतः प्रभावितयन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <option>[General]</option> section has the following options:"
msgstr ""
"द<option value=[General]> [सामान्य]</option> विभागे निम्नलिखितविकल्पाः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckSycoca"
msgstr "चेकसाइकोका"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to update sycoca at startup (default: <constant>true</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"प्रारम्भे sycoca अद्यतनं कर्तव्यं वा (पूर्वनिर्धारितं: <constant>true</constant>) ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckUpdates"
msgstr "CheckUpdates"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to perform outstanding KConfig updates at startup (default: "
"<constant>true</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"प्रारम्भे बकाया KConfig अद्यतनं कर्तव्यं वा (पूर्वनिर्धारितं: <constant>true</constant>) "
"।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckFileStamps"
msgstr "चेकफाइलस्टैम्प्स"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to check file timestamps when performing the initial sycoca update "
"(default: <constant>true</constant>). See the documentation for "
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> for more details."
msgstr ""
"प्रारम्भिकं sycoca अद्यतनं कुर्वन् सञ्चिकासमयमुद्राणां जाँचः करणीयः वा (पूर्वनिर्धारितम्: "
"<constant>true</constant>) । अधिकविवरणार्थं <command>kbuildsycoca6</command> "
"इत्यस्य दस्तावेजीकरणं पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "DelayedCheck"
msgstr "विलम्बितपरीक्षण"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to delay the initial sycoca update until about a minute after "
"starting (default: <constant>false</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"आरम्भस्य sycoca अद्यतनं आरम्भस्य प्रायः एकनिमेषपर्यन्तं विलम्बितव्यं वा (पूर्वनिर्धारितम्: "
"<constant>false</constant>) ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:118
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Each module also has a <option>[Module-<replaceable>name</replaceable>]</"
#| "option> section in <filename>kded6rc</filename>, where <replaceable>name</"
#| "replaceable> is the name of the module's desktop file without the "
#| "<filename>.desktop</filename> extension. This contains an "
#| "<option>autoload</option> option that specifies whether the module should "
#| "be automatically loaded when <command>kded6</command> is started "
#| "(default: <constant>false</constant>). Note that this setting can also be "
#| "changed via <command>kded6</command>'s &DBus; interface."
msgid ""
"Each module also has a <option>[Module-<replaceable>name</replaceable>]</"
"option> section in <filename>kded5rc</filename>, where <replaceable>name</"
"replaceable> is the name of the module's desktop file without the <filename>."
"desktop</filename> extension. This contains an <option>autoload</option> "
"option that specifies whether the module should be automatically loaded when "
"<command>kded6</command> is started (default: <constant>false</constant>). "
"Note that this setting can also be changed via <command>kded6</command>'s "
"&DBus; interface."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकं मॉड्यूले अपि क<option> [मॉड्यूल- ९.<replaceable> नामः</replaceable> ] .</"
"option> खण्डः in<filename> kded6rc</filename> , कुत्र<replaceable> नामः</"
"replaceable> विना मॉड्यूलस्य डेस्कटॉप् सञ्चिकायाः नाम अस्ति<filename> .डेस्कटॉप्</"
"filename> विस्तार। अस्मिन् अन्<option value=autoload> autoload इति</option> "
"विकल्पः यः निर्दिशति यत् मॉड्यूलः स्वयमेव कदा लोड् कर्तव्यः वा इति<command> kded6</"
"command> आरब्धम् अस्ति (पूर्वनिर्धारितम्:<constant> असत्य</constant> ). ध्यानं कुर्वन्तु "
"यत् एतत् सेटिङ्ग् मार्गेण अपि परिवर्तयितुं शक्यते<command> kded6</command> &#39;s &amp;"
"DBus; अन्तरफलकम् ।"

